OL,3,CRecent sightings bring renewed hope
OL,4,Cfor missing capybara
OL,6,FChief Executive of Marwell, Laura
OL,7,FRead, gives an update on the
OL,8,Fcontinuing search.
OL,10,FKeepers at Marwell Zoo are refusing to
OL,11,Fgive up hope of recapturing Samba the
OL,12,Ffugitive capybara.
OL,14,FShe escaped from her pen on March
OL,15,F17th, but three months on remains on
OL,16,Fthe run in the local area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
