OL,3,CRecent sightings bring renewed hope
OL,4,Cfor missing capybara
OL,6,FThere have been several 'credible'
OL,7,Fsightings in the Brambridge area over
OL,8,Frecent days, with more than 20 members
OL,9,Fof the Marwell team responding with a
OL,10,Fcoordinated ground search.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the zoo's chief
OL,13,FExecutive Laura Read said additional
OL,14,Fcamera traps had been deployed in the
OL,15,Farea:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780834280
OL,3,CRecent sightings bring renewed hope
OL,4,Cfor missing capybara
OL,6,F"While our thermal drones and camera
OL,7,Ftrap network continue to play a vital
OL,8,Frole in the search for Samba, putting
OL,9,Flarge numbers of people on the ground
OL,10,Fis only effective when we have
OL,11,Fspecific, recent information about
OL,12,Fwhere she may be.
OL,14,F"With these latest reports providing a
OL,15,Fmuch narrower search area, our teams
OL,16,Fhave been looking for footprints,
OL,17,Fdroppings and any direct signs of
OL,18,FSamba's presence."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780834280
OL,3,CRecent sightings bring renewed hope
OL,4,Cfor missing capybara
OL,6,FShe said the vegetation in the area
OL,7,Fwas extremely dense, making the search
OL,8,Fparticularly challenging.
OL,10,F"Unfortunately, despite today's
OL,11,Fextensive efforts, our teams were
OL,12,Fstill unable to locate Samba," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"However, the recent sightings have
OL,16,Fhelped us significantly narrow down
OL,17,Fthe search area and we remain hopeful."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
