OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780834280
OL,3,CRecent sightings bring renewed hope
OL,4,Cfor missing capybara
OL,6,FShe thanked the community for their
OL,7,Fcontinuing support and vigilance, and
OL,8,Fsaid Samba's welfare remains the
OL,9,Fabsolute priority. "We are continuing
OL,10,Fto use every appropriate tool
OL,11,Favailable to help us locate her and
OL,12,Fbring her safely back to Marwell," she
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FIf you believe you may have seen
OL,16,FSamba, please:
OL,18,F Take a photo
OL,20,F Send it to 07436 116740
